    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "One may want to accept different numbers of confirmations in different contexts. Wait 100 confirmations for a house. 1 or even 0 for a coffee. OTOH it's already possible to wait any number of confirmations that you want before acting on a transaction. The 6 recommended transactions are just a quick visual indication.\n\nI'm generally against adding options, if we added an option for everything bitcoiners hairsplitting over then we'd have an options pane like the space shuttle cockpit. But in this case if it affects coin selection as well as display I'm not against it.\n",
